    "Anything on your mind. You can talk about stress, anxiety, relationships, sleep, work, or just how your day went. You can also tap one of the conversation starters if you're not sure where to begin." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "أي شيء في ذهنك. يمكنك التحدث عن التوتر أو القلق أو العلاقات أو النوم أو العمل أو فقط كيف كان يومك. يمكنك أيضاً النقر على أحد بوادر المحادثة إذا لم تكن متأكداً من أين تبدأ."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "Anything on your mind. You can talk about stress, anxiety, relationships, sleep, work, or just how your day went. You can also tap one of the conversation starters if you're not sure where to begin."
          }
        }
      }
    },
